<cb:div type="xuzang-notes">
<head>卍續藏 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0629j01" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_jie" target="#nkr_note_orig_jie_0629j01">但除生滅即當下涅槃何待生後耆婆此云長壽觀河之眼則有童耄昏明觀河之見則無老少此意令文不見却又露在面皺中</note>
<note n="0629j02" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_jie" target="#nkr_note_orig_jie_0629j02">悲不先期名海潮音</note>
<note n="0630j01" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_jie" target="#nkr_note_orig_jie_0630j01">拘舍離外道六師之一為塵謝心滅為冥諦塵對心生為覺諦彼正不知也</note>
<note n="0630j02" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_jie" target="#nkr_note_orig_jie_0630j02">如第二月猶有所還如月影者則是前塵影事幻妄非真決決不可認以為心明矣</note>
<note n="0630j03" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_jie" target="#nkr_note_orig_jie_0630j03">吾之見是我所獨見彼如何見得若能見得是我之見將與物同而我之見豈物類乎</note>
<note n="0631001" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0631001">性疑惟次同</note>
<note n="0632j01" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_jie" target="#nkr_note_orig_jie_0632j01">妙絕</note>
<note n="0632j02" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_jie" target="#nkr_note_orig_jie_0632j02">目食曰通珮玦妖氣近日之象呈芒遍指曰彗四出曰孛絕迹而去日飛光迹相連曰流妖氣背日如負旁日如旦明為虹暗為蜺</note>
</p>
